			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n2. goto 55.273; 42.457; -93.8\r\n3. CTRL-Shift-K on the NPC to kill it\r\n4. create OBJ_Scroll_SpeakWithDead 10\r\n5. Use the scroll on the corpse.\r\n\r\nThe player is the killer - \r\n1. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n2. goto 55.273; 42.457; -93.8\r\n3. Attack the npc and kill it\r\n4. create OBJ_Scroll_SpeakWithDead 10\r\n5. Use the scroll on the corpse.."
				},
